[31/12/2016 03:13:22] <font color="#00ff00">¿Quieres avergonzarme?</font>
[31/12/2016 03:13:31] <font color="#00ff00">Ahora vete.</font>
[31/12/2016 03:13:38] <font color="#00ff00">Me llamo Yusuf.</font>
[31/12/2016 03:13:41] <font color="#ffff00">Lo sé.</font>
[31/12/2016 03:13:41] <font color="#ffff00">Yo me llamo...</font>
